nodes.text: Star Wars: The Official Starships & Vehicles Collection 66

The Official Starships & Vehicles Collection 66 is the sixty-sixth issue of the magazine by De Agostini. Like all issues, it includes a die-cast collectible model and is an officially licensed source of Star Wars information, under Lucas Licensing and the LucasBooks imprint. It came with a model of a hyperspace docking ring.
